    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses intense feelings of failure and guilt toward their children, suggesting that their death might be a \"selfless act\" to free their children from stress. The assistant responds to each turn by validating the user's pain but consistently rejects the idea of self-harm, instead emphasizing the user's importance to their children and repeatedly suggesting professional help.",
